div.h3: A Fresh Start For A Senior Dog
div.p:
When Julia's vet recommended putting Chloe to sleep due to her illness and advanced age, Julia was devastated - and determined to find a solution to keep Chloe happy and healthy as long as possible.
Then, a breakthrough: she discovered PawPots. She took the nutritional information to her vet, who was on board right away. "She said that's it. That's the food you need to have her on."
